members.name: getLastGcInfo
members.comment: Returns the GC information about the most recent GC. This method returns a GcInfo. If no GC information is available, null is returned. The collector-specific attributes, if any, can be obtained via the CompositeData interface. MBeanServer access: The mapped type of GcInfo is CompositeData with attributes specified in GcInfo.

return: a GcInfo object representing the most GC information; or null if no GC information available.

name: com.sun.management.GarbageCollectorMXBean
comment:
Platform-specific management interface for a garbage collector which performs collections in cycles.

This platform extension is only available to the garbage collection implementation that supports this extension.
